1
00:00:09,240 --> 00:00:10,380
My back!

2
00:00:11,510 --> 00:00:12,090
Mr. Chen.

3
00:00:12,350 --> 00:00:13,940
Mr. Chen, what are you doing?

4
00:00:20,710 --> 00:00:21,530
Chen Shenglong

5
00:00:23,120 --> 00:00:24,420
used judicial means

6
00:00:25,510 --> 00:00:26,940
to completely crush his opponents.

7
00:00:36,200 --> 00:00:38,010
My wife Liu Yun is the deputy director
of the Development Zone.

8
00:00:39,670 --> 00:00:42,620
She helped Chen Shenglong
acquire Wanchuan Mining.

9
00:00:43,960 --> 00:00:44,620
And I was

10
00:00:45,790 --> 00:00:46,940
in charge of the Wan Hai case.

11
00:00:49,070 --> 00:00:51,620
Do I look like the protector
of Tianlong Company?

12
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:20,480
[In the Name of Justice]

13
00:02:20,480 --> 00:02:23,480
[Episode 24]

14
00:02:28,030 --> 00:02:31,570
Now, we'll give you an update
on the accident rescue work

15
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:32,820
at Wanchuan Mining.

16
00:02:32,840 --> 00:02:33,520
[Press Conference on the
Emergency Response at Wanchuan Mining]

17
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:33,940
Please welcome

18
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:37,290
the Deputy Director of Pingshan
Development Zone Managing Committee,

19
00:02:37,710 --> 00:02:38,660
Liu Yun.

20
00:02:41,080 --> 00:02:43,260
At 7:37 PM on May 16th

21
00:02:44,150 --> 00:02:45,500
in Dongping City, Haidong Province,

22
00:02:46,080 --> 00:02:47,980
a lifting cage accident occurred

23
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:51,660
at Wanchuan Mining's Mine No. 18.

24
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:54,500
There were 15 people
inside the cage at the time,

25
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:56,100
all trapped underground.

26
00:02:56,750 --> 00:02:57,610
After the accident,

27
00:02:58,030 --> 00:03:00,060
the Dongping Municipal Government
attached great importance to it,

28
00:03:00,870 --> 00:03:03,660
immediately activating
a Level II emergency response,

29
00:03:04,870 --> 00:03:07,380
establishing a municipal-level
on-site command center,

30
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:10,130
and formulating a rescue plan.

31
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,730
Rescue operations have been
carried out with full effort.

32
00:03:13,470 --> 00:03:14,220
As of now,

33
00:03:14,590 --> 00:03:16,010
all the injured have been rescued

34
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:18,540
and sent to the hospital for treatment.

35
00:03:19,190 --> 00:03:19,610
Among them,

36
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:22,060
two people have been confirmed dead.

37
00:03:22,750 --> 00:03:23,660
The remaining 13

38
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:25,380
have all been out of danger.

39
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:27,100
Six of them are severely injured,

40
00:03:27,430 --> 00:03:28,290
and seven have minor injuries.

41
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:30,010
In terms of aftermath handling,

42
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:32,450
the Development Zone Managing Committee
has assigned a dedicated team

43
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:33,690
to form a working group,

44
00:03:34,150 --> 00:03:35,060
which will ensure

45
00:03:35,150 --> 00:03:37,290
survivors' families receive
timely and compassionate support.

46
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:38,660
Regarding

47
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:41,540
the cause of the lifting cage's fall,

48
00:03:42,150 --> 00:03:44,010
the Public Security Bureau
and the Emergency Management Bureau

49
00:03:44,150 --> 00:03:45,290
have launched an investigation.

50
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:46,940
Preliminary findings indicate that

51
00:03:47,190 --> 00:03:50,690
the accident was caused by
aging of the traction system

52
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:53,730
and long-term overcapacity operation.

53
00:03:54,630 --> 00:03:56,410
Despite repeated warnings,

54
00:03:56,910 --> 00:03:58,100
the company continued
illegal mining activities

55
00:03:58,960 --> 00:03:59,660
and refused to carry out rectifications,

56
00:04:00,150 --> 00:04:02,940
which ultimately led to
this work safety accident.

57
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:03,780
At present,

58
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:05,660
the individual responsible, Mr. Wan,

59
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:08,220
is being actively pursued.

60
00:04:08,590 --> 00:04:10,980
We will continue to release
case information

61
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:13,010
in a timely and accurate manner

62
00:04:13,470 --> 00:04:14,380
and launch

63
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:18,930
a region-wide work safety
inspection and rectification.

64
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:20,730
Mr. Chen, Mr. Wan's here.

65
00:04:23,070 --> 00:04:23,930
Our honored guest.

66
00:04:23,950 --> 00:04:24,610
Mr. Chen…

67
00:04:24,630 --> 00:04:25,170
Mr. Wan…

68
00:04:25,190 --> 00:04:25,700
Welcome…

69
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:27,250
Sorry to call you over at this hour.

70
00:04:27,510 --> 00:04:28,100
It's alright.

71
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:28,660
Come on in.

72
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:29,490
First time at the company, right?

73
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:31,170
Mr. Chen, what's going on here?

74
00:04:31,750 --> 00:04:33,050
I'll give you a proper tour in a bit.

75
00:04:33,630 --> 00:04:34,490
I bet you haven't had a decent meal

76
00:04:34,510 --> 00:04:35,930
since the accident.

77
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:37,700
This is our favorite food.

78
00:04:38,070 --> 00:04:38,370
Come on.

79
00:04:38,390 --> 00:04:38,850
Okay.

80
00:04:38,950 --> 00:04:39,580
Eat while it's hot.

81
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:42,140
Mr. Chen, you're doing pretty well.

82
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:43,340
Impressive.

83
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:43,850
Mr. Wan,

84
00:04:43,870 --> 00:04:44,780
here, eat up.

85
00:04:44,950 --> 00:04:45,490
Don't mind if I do.

86
00:04:45,510 --> 00:04:46,050
Hurry…

87
00:04:46,070 --> 00:04:46,660
Come on…

88
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:47,490
Okay…

89
00:04:55,160 --> 00:04:55,700
Mr. Wan,

90
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:57,700
how are things at the hospital?

91
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:01,810
Don't mention it.

92
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:04,900
Two dead.

93
00:05:05,750 --> 00:05:06,660
Some of them

94
00:05:06,830 --> 00:05:07,930
survived,

95
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:09,810
but they're basically done for.

96
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:12,700
To be honest,

97
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:14,460
for the dead ones,

98
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:16,020
I can at least put a number
on the compensation.

99
00:05:16,190 --> 00:05:17,460
But for the injured ones?

100
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:19,100
There's no end to it,

101
00:05:19,270 --> 00:05:20,700
it's gonna be like a black hole.

102
00:05:22,390 --> 00:05:23,370
I'm so screwed.

103
00:05:23,390 --> 00:05:24,490
Can't believe this happened to me.

104
00:05:24,750 --> 00:05:25,290
Mr. Wan,

105
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:26,980
don't be upset.

106
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:29,580
What did the government say?

107
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:31,050
What can they say?

108
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:32,730
They're pressuring me to pay the families.

109
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:35,220
Mr. Chen,

110
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:38,660
you know I'm broke.

111
00:05:39,270 --> 00:05:40,410
What do I have to pay with?

112
00:05:41,360 --> 00:05:42,610
It's not that
I don't want to compensate,

113
00:05:43,510 --> 00:05:43,930
I just…

114
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:45,850
I can't.

115
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:48,410
It's driving me crazy.

116
00:05:49,270 --> 00:05:50,050
How much are they asking?

117
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:51,850
Some want a million.

118
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:53,900
And some even want two.

119
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:55,900
They're insane.

120
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:57,370
Tell me, is my life even
worth a million?

121
00:05:57,750 --> 00:05:59,490
If you think it is,

122
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:00,220
take it,

123
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:01,370
go ahead.

124
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:03,850
If it comes to that,

125
00:06:04,390 --> 00:06:05,580
I've got nothing left to lose.

126
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:06,220
Screw it.

127
00:06:06,310 --> 00:06:06,980
I'm done.

128
00:06:08,430 --> 00:06:08,900
Mr. Wan,

129
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:11,050
don't worry.

130
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,290
I'll help you

131
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:15,580
carry this burden.

132
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:17,020
Mr. Chen, thank you.

133
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:18,850
Don't try to make me feel better.

134
00:06:19,270 --> 00:06:20,340
I'll cover the compensation.

135
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:23,140
Whatever the families ask for,
I'll handle it.

136
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:30,810
You'll do that?

137
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:32,290
While I'm at it,

138
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:34,700
I'll pay off your bank loans too.

139
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:37,170
The money's ready.

140
00:06:37,750 --> 00:06:39,730
Here's the deal, talk to your brother,

141
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:41,370
have him hand the mine over to me.

142
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:43,700
The loans are massive,

143
00:06:43,870 --> 00:06:44,730
and with all the interest,

144
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:46,020
there's no way you'll ever
pay them back.

145
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:47,220
Also…

146
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:03,730
Kick a man when he's down.

147
00:07:07,390 --> 00:07:08,370
Capitalize on a bad situation.

148
00:07:10,270 --> 00:07:12,660
Mr. Chen, you may as well
just rob me outright.

149
00:07:14,830 --> 00:07:15,340
Mr. Wan.

150
00:07:16,510 --> 00:07:18,700
You let your brother give me the mine,

151
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:22,370
you can ask me for whatever you want.

152
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:23,370
Mr. Chen,

153
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:25,290
thanks for the food.

154
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:26,170
Really.

155
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:27,980
But there's a pile of mess
at the hospital

156
00:07:28,070 --> 00:07:28,850
waiting for me.

157
00:07:28,870 --> 00:07:29,490
I need to be there.

158
00:07:29,950 --> 00:07:30,610
So I'm gonna head back now.

159
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:35,580
As for the mine,

160
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:36,780
you don't even need to ask my brother.

161
00:07:37,510 --> 00:07:38,460
I won't agree to it.

162
00:07:39,950 --> 00:07:40,900
Forget it.

163
00:07:42,390 --> 00:07:42,780
Goodbye.

164
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:46,050
Did we say you can leave?

165
00:07:46,630 --> 00:07:47,810
We're not done talking!

166
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:50,100
Why so worked up?

167
00:07:52,070 --> 00:07:52,900
We'll talk later.

168
00:07:55,630 --> 00:07:56,220
Where do you think you're going?

169
00:07:56,270 --> 00:07:56,610
Go back.

170
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:57,370
Back.

171
00:07:57,390 --> 00:07:58,170
No, get out of my way.

172
00:07:58,240 --> 00:07:59,170
Go back!

173
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:01,410
Freeze!

174
00:08:02,270 --> 00:08:02,660
Don't move.

175
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:03,540
What are you doing?

176
00:08:08,430 --> 00:08:09,580
My back!

177
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:11,140
Let me go!

178
00:08:11,720 --> 00:08:12,290
Mr. Chen.

179
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:14,140
Mr. Chen, what are you doing?

180
00:08:15,270 --> 00:08:16,290
You know, I've got a back injury!

181
00:08:18,750 --> 00:08:19,370
Go on then.

182
00:08:19,630 --> 00:08:21,220
Just kill me.

183
00:08:21,560 --> 00:08:22,250
Kill me.

184
00:08:22,830 --> 00:08:23,850
I don't even care anymore.

185
00:08:24,310 --> 00:08:25,020
Just kill me.

186
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:28,290
That lifting cage

187
00:08:28,750 --> 00:08:29,850
in your mine

188
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:31,930
fell down just like that.

189
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:36,650
Do you know why?

190
00:08:40,670 --> 00:08:43,300
Because the winch had no brake force.

191
00:08:46,390 --> 00:08:47,250
And why did it

192
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:49,650
have no brake force?

193
00:08:51,870 --> 00:08:52,820
That's because

194
00:08:54,120 --> 00:08:56,420
it had no brake fluid.

195
00:08:58,390 --> 00:09:01,370
Why did it have no brake fluid?

196
00:09:06,270 --> 00:09:07,530
Because

197
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:10,700
I drained it.

198
00:09:14,670 --> 00:09:15,490
You'd better

199
00:09:15,870 --> 00:09:17,130
hand that mine over

200
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:19,060
willingly.

201
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:21,250
And I promise

202
00:09:22,390 --> 00:09:23,370
it won't happen again.

203
00:09:24,790 --> 00:09:25,530
Or else,

204
00:09:27,150 --> 00:09:29,300
I really don't know what I'll do.

205
00:09:49,030 --> 00:09:49,530
Mr. Wan,

206
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:54,250
your company's legal representative
is Wan Chao, right?

207
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:57,490
He's vanished

208
00:09:58,000 --> 00:09:59,220
since the accident.

209
00:10:01,510 --> 00:10:02,420
Let me make this very clear,

210
00:10:03,550 --> 00:10:04,420
if your brother

211
00:10:04,910 --> 00:10:06,180
doesn't agree to give me the mine,

212
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:07,650
then Wan Chao's life

213
00:10:08,910 --> 00:10:09,940
is in God's hands.

214
00:10:19,030 --> 00:10:19,530
Everyone,

215
00:10:20,030 --> 00:10:21,220
Zhang Fang

216
00:10:21,790 --> 00:10:23,060
reported issues uncovered

217
00:10:23,720 --> 00:10:24,580
by the procuratorate

218
00:10:25,150 --> 00:10:25,700
during the investigation

219
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:28,460
of the Wan Hai case

220
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:30,100
in Dongping.

221
00:10:30,910 --> 00:10:31,340
These include

222
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:32,820
whether the Wan Hai case

223
00:10:33,510 --> 00:10:36,060
qualifies as an organized crime case,

224
00:10:36,550 --> 00:10:37,130
and whether

225
00:10:37,630 --> 00:10:39,650
there are duty-related crimes behind it.

226
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:40,730
There are

227
00:10:41,670 --> 00:10:43,490
now clear leads.

228
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:45,850
What are your thoughts?

229
00:10:46,510 --> 00:10:47,160
[Hao Dongliang]
This case

230
00:10:47,160 --> 00:10:47,960
[Vice Governor of Haidong Province
and Head of Public Security Bureau]

231
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:49,770
has drawn major attention
from the province.

232
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:51,300
And right after it wrapped up,

233
00:10:51,790 --> 00:10:52,730
a mine accident occurred.

234
00:10:52,910 --> 00:10:54,300
Now we've uncovered even more problems,

235
00:10:54,960 --> 00:10:55,650
it's definitely fishy.

236
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:57,650
Among them,

237
00:10:58,320 --> 00:10:59,770
we even found indications
of criminal offense.

238
00:11:00,480 --> 00:11:02,650
When it comes to the hidden
duty-related crimes,

239
00:11:02,870 --> 00:11:03,850
the Public Security Bureau
of Haidong Province

240
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:06,180
should work closely
with the procuratorate.

241
00:11:06,550 --> 00:11:08,010
We should crack down on
all criminal offenses

242
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:10,180
with severe measures,
leaving none unchecked.

243
00:11:10,750 --> 00:11:13,220
From a perspective of
handling and hearing a case,

244
00:11:13,790 --> 00:11:15,460
accountability is now lifelong.

245
00:11:15,720 --> 00:11:16,120
[Zheng Zhong
President of Haidong Senior People Court]

246
00:11:16,120 --> 00:11:16,940
The earlier we detect,

247
00:11:17,240 --> 00:11:18,010
address,

248
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:18,890
and correct problems,

249
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:20,300
the less passive we become.

250
00:11:20,910 --> 00:11:23,220
It's also about taking responsibilities.

251
00:11:23,840 --> 00:11:24,250
My suggestion is,

252
00:11:24,870 --> 00:11:25,700
hold on to the case,

253
00:11:26,120 --> 00:11:26,940
get to the bottom of it.

254
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:30,100
Zhang Fang, what do you think?

255
00:11:32,320 --> 00:11:33,530
According to
the Supreme People's Procuratorate,

256
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:35,460
leave no criminal unpunished,

257
00:11:36,240 --> 00:11:37,580
don't wrongfully accuse
anyone who's not involved.

258
00:11:38,510 --> 00:11:38,980
Since

259
00:11:39,630 --> 00:11:40,940
there are problems
with the Wan Hai case,

260
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:42,420
we will initiate a reinvestigation.

261
00:11:42,910 --> 00:11:43,940
As for

262
00:11:44,720 --> 00:11:45,650
the suspected duty-related crimes

263
00:11:45,670 --> 00:11:46,980
committed by state functionaries,

264
00:11:47,440 --> 00:11:49,770
we must also investigate resolutely

265
00:11:50,030 --> 00:11:51,580
under the central government's
directives

266
00:11:52,510 --> 00:11:53,370
to strengthen prosecutorial oversight.

267
00:11:53,840 --> 00:11:54,980
This involves

268
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:57,370
criminal investigations
by the public security organs

269
00:11:58,030 --> 00:11:58,730
and

270
00:11:59,200 --> 00:12:00,060
investigations into duty-related crimes

271
00:12:00,360 --> 00:12:01,850
by the disciplinary

272
00:12:01,870 --> 00:12:02,980
and supervisory authorities.

273
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:05,130
We'll need to coordinate
across these bodies.

274
00:12:07,030 --> 00:12:08,490
Does anyone else have comments?

275
00:12:10,680 --> 00:12:12,760
[Yan Licheng, Hao Dongliang, Zhang Fang]

276
00:12:17,960 --> 00:12:18,490
Yesterday,

277
00:12:20,360 --> 00:12:21,940
after receiving the report
from the Provincial Procuratorate,

278
00:12:23,360 --> 00:12:24,980
I recognized the seriousness
of the issue

279
00:12:25,960 --> 00:12:28,730
and reported it to Secretary He Zhigang
of the Provincial Party Committee.

280
00:12:29,960 --> 00:12:30,850
Mr. He gave clear instructions

281
00:12:32,270 --> 00:12:32,820
that the Central Government

282
00:12:33,750 --> 00:12:35,580
places great importance

283
00:12:36,240 --> 00:12:37,010
on the anti-organized crime campaign,

284
00:12:38,480 --> 00:12:40,420
and even greater emphasis on
work style construction,

285
00:12:40,790 --> 00:12:42,100
which has been a priority

286
00:12:42,790 --> 00:12:43,820
since the 18th CPC National Congress.

