00:24:48,510 --> 00:24:49,530
I did as Zhang Wenjing said.

572
00:24:49,550 --> 00:24:51,050
I hired some guys
to beat Wang Yu into submission,

573
00:24:51,240 --> 00:24:53,330
and then forced him to sign the contract.

574
00:24:53,510 --> 00:24:55,330
She drafted the contract.

575
00:24:55,680 --> 00:24:56,620
And when my club's head of security

576
00:24:56,830 --> 00:24:58,250
crippled that man,

577
00:24:58,880 --> 00:25:01,220
she arranged the false testimony

578
00:25:02,200 --> 00:25:03,330
to cover me.

579
00:25:03,440 --> 00:25:04,620
I am a gangster.

580
00:25:06,640 --> 00:25:07,460
I'll always be.

581
00:25:08,590 --> 00:25:09,620
Defendant Wan Hai,

582
00:25:10,070 --> 00:25:10,980
the court sentences you

583
00:25:11,240 --> 00:25:12,900
to a combined prison term

584
00:25:13,110 --> 00:25:15,980
of 10 years and 10 months
for multiple crimes.

585
00:25:20,400 --> 00:25:21,010
You know what,

586
00:25:23,830 --> 00:25:25,180
you go tell Yu Tiancheng,

587
00:25:26,960 --> 00:25:28,140
if he wants to kill me,

588
00:25:28,310 --> 00:25:30,180
he doesn't have to go through all this.

589
00:25:30,400 --> 00:25:32,090
Sentencing me to ten years and ten months?

590
00:25:32,240 --> 00:25:33,620
So he's been plotting this

591
00:25:33,640 --> 00:25:35,010
for three years.

592
00:25:35,640 --> 00:25:36,250
I can sell the mine

593
00:25:37,000 --> 00:25:38,010
to anyone,

594
00:25:38,270 --> 00:25:39,530
except him.

595
00:25:39,960 --> 00:25:40,900
Pass that along

596
00:25:41,960 --> 00:25:44,330
to Chen Shenglong,
let Chen Shenglong tell him.

597
00:25:47,590 --> 00:25:48,140
Wait, brother…

598
00:25:49,240 --> 00:25:50,730
what exactly is going on
between you two

599
00:25:50,750 --> 00:25:51,490
that I don't know about?

600
00:26:00,440 --> 00:26:00,770
Bro…

601
00:26:01,510 --> 00:26:01,860
Brother.

602
00:26:04,510 --> 00:26:04,860
I…

603
00:26:06,350 --> 00:26:07,700
I can't take it any longer.

604
00:26:11,240 --> 00:26:12,250
I just can't.

605
00:26:13,510 --> 00:26:15,530
You don't know how ruthless
Chen Shenglong is.

606
00:26:17,270 --> 00:26:19,180
Whatever he wants, he gets.

607
00:26:20,400 --> 00:26:21,570
He'll do anything.

608
00:26:21,590 --> 00:26:22,940
We can't fight him.

609
00:26:26,310 --> 00:26:28,290
That press conference just declared it

610
00:26:28,400 --> 00:26:31,140
a work safety accident,

611
00:26:31,960 --> 00:26:33,250
and then he told me right away

612
00:26:33,680 --> 00:26:34,730
he did it.

613
00:26:35,400 --> 00:26:37,980
If he can get you convicted
as a gangster,

614
00:26:38,960 --> 00:26:40,460
what else can't he do?

615
00:26:43,640 --> 00:26:45,330
I'm so sorry for what happened

616
00:26:46,160 --> 00:26:47,220
at your mine.

617
00:26:48,350 --> 00:26:49,620
Looks like our public security efforts

618
00:26:49,640 --> 00:26:50,700
still need

619
00:26:51,510 --> 00:26:52,460
improvement.

620
00:26:52,550 --> 00:26:53,940
We fell short

621
00:26:54,480 --> 00:26:54,980
in many aspects.

622
00:26:55,310 --> 00:26:55,940
Captain Sun,

623
00:26:56,590 --> 00:26:57,620
we don't blame you.

624
00:26:58,510 --> 00:27:01,330
Those guys from the neighboring mine
are too aggressive.

625
00:27:01,480 --> 00:27:02,860
They weren't just after money.

626
00:27:03,110 --> 00:27:05,050
They wanted my life. My mine.

627
00:27:05,070 --> 00:27:05,490
Mr. Wan.

628
00:27:05,880 --> 00:27:07,290
Mr. Wan, calm down.

629
00:27:08,830 --> 00:27:10,220
I've heard about the rivalry

630
00:27:11,590 --> 00:27:12,570
between your companies.

631
00:27:12,750 --> 00:27:14,050
But to be honest,

632
00:27:14,200 --> 00:27:15,050
and I hope you won't take offense,

633
00:27:15,310 --> 00:27:17,140
it takes two to tango.

634
00:27:18,550 --> 00:27:20,290
This can't keep going on

635
00:27:20,640 --> 00:27:21,460
forever.

636
00:27:21,830 --> 00:27:23,180
Now that I'm here today,

637
00:27:24,110 --> 00:27:25,250
I'd like to help address

638
00:27:25,270 --> 00:27:26,530
the real root of the problem.

639
00:27:26,880 --> 00:27:28,490
How do you plan to do that?

640
00:27:29,440 --> 00:27:30,140
Listen to me.

641
00:27:32,590 --> 00:27:33,330
Wait, where are you going?

642
00:27:36,880 --> 00:27:37,760
Mr. Yu, come on.

643
00:27:37,760 --> 00:27:39,520
[Office]

644
00:27:39,520 --> 00:27:39,810
Come.

645
00:27:41,030 --> 00:27:41,420
Come here.

646
00:27:45,720 --> 00:27:46,530
Say it. Apologize.

647
00:27:46,680 --> 00:27:47,220
Say you're sorry.

648
00:27:49,720 --> 00:27:50,290
Mr. Wan.

649
00:27:58,270 --> 00:28:01,010
I am here to apologize to you.

650
00:28:04,350 --> 00:28:05,530
Wait, what's he doing here?

651
00:28:05,640 --> 00:28:06,700
I know

652
00:28:07,160 --> 00:28:09,490
you two have been
at each other's throats

653
00:28:09,590 --> 00:28:10,220
for years.

654
00:28:10,440 --> 00:28:12,330
But let's be honest,

655
00:28:13,160 --> 00:28:13,620
well,

656
00:28:14,240 --> 00:28:15,330
the things you did at the mine

657
00:28:15,880 --> 00:28:17,290
weren't any better than his.

658
00:28:17,590 --> 00:28:18,700
If we really dig deep,

659
00:28:18,720 --> 00:28:20,250
neither side will come out on top.

660
00:28:20,270 --> 00:28:21,330
What are you saying?

661
00:28:22,160 --> 00:28:23,860
He killed two people at my mine.

662
00:28:24,000 --> 00:28:24,940
How dare you try to help a murderer?

663
00:28:25,110 --> 00:28:27,140
And I almost got shot.

664
00:28:27,310 --> 00:28:28,810
I won't just let this go!

665
00:28:29,030 --> 00:28:30,380
Do you still want to keep
doing business in Dongping?

666
00:28:30,640 --> 00:28:31,490
Are you threatening me?

667
00:28:32,110 --> 00:28:33,090
I'm reminding you.

668
00:28:33,110 --> 00:28:34,330
A kind reminder.

669
00:28:34,350 --> 00:28:36,220
I believe there's justice in Dongping!

670
00:28:36,790 --> 00:28:37,460
I'm done talking to you.

671
00:28:38,240 --> 00:28:38,810
Get lost.

672
00:28:40,200 --> 00:28:40,770
I'll sue you.

673
00:28:43,960 --> 00:28:44,330
Brother,

674
00:28:50,070 --> 00:28:50,490
he said

675
00:28:51,640 --> 00:28:53,050
if we refuse to sell the mine,

676
00:28:54,160 --> 00:28:55,140
then Chao's life

677
00:28:55,400 --> 00:28:56,570
is as good as gone.

678
00:28:58,350 --> 00:29:00,460
We can't risk Chao.

679
00:29:03,640 --> 00:29:04,980
We have to survive, brother.

680
00:29:05,790 --> 00:29:06,180
Brother.

681
00:29:10,350 --> 00:29:11,140
Please…

682
00:29:26,920 --> 00:29:27,570
Mr. Xudong,

683
00:29:28,640 --> 00:29:29,330
have some late-night snack.

684
00:29:30,160 --> 00:29:31,140
Liang, your phone.

685
00:29:38,590 --> 00:29:39,140
Ma'am.

686
00:29:40,000 --> 00:29:40,980
Did you finish packing?

687
00:29:41,110 --> 00:29:42,700
When are you planning to come over?

688
00:29:47,270 --> 00:29:47,570
I…

689
00:29:48,720 --> 00:29:49,090
I need to

690
00:29:49,550 --> 00:29:51,180
report something to you.

691
00:29:52,750 --> 00:29:53,090
Go on.

692
00:29:55,550 --> 00:29:56,010
Well,

693
00:29:57,480 --> 00:29:58,570
I need to go on

694
00:29:59,440 --> 00:30:00,250
a business trip.

695
00:30:01,160 --> 00:30:01,770
Once it's done,

696
00:30:02,480 --> 00:30:03,050
I'll come join you.

697
00:30:03,240 --> 00:30:04,530
Hong Liang, give me a straight answer.

698
00:30:04,550 --> 00:30:05,770
Are you coming or not?

699
00:30:06,200 --> 00:30:08,180
If you're not,
then I'll just let this go.

700
00:30:08,750 --> 00:30:09,460
But if you are,

701
00:30:09,480 --> 00:30:10,810
stop making excuses every time.

702
00:30:12,680 --> 00:30:13,490
Don't get mad.

703
00:30:13,510 --> 00:30:15,090
I'm just telling you this news.

704
00:30:15,720 --> 00:30:16,330
If you're not okay with it,

705
00:30:16,440 --> 00:30:17,010
then I'll just

706
00:30:17,400 --> 00:30:18,570
turn this down.

707
00:30:18,960 --> 00:30:19,860
I'll cancel the trip

708
00:30:20,030 --> 00:30:22,290
and come straight to you. How's that?

709
00:30:22,440 --> 00:30:23,180
You said it.

710
00:30:23,960 --> 00:30:24,980
Then I'm booking your ticket right now.

711
00:30:25,350 --> 00:30:27,050
Hong Liang, be honest with me.

712
00:30:27,400 --> 00:30:29,090
You don't want to
come to Beijing at all, do you?

713
00:30:29,680 --> 00:30:30,050
No, I…

714
00:30:30,510 --> 00:30:31,420
What did I say tonight

715
00:30:31,830 --> 00:30:34,220
to make you think that?

716
00:30:34,240 --> 00:30:35,860
Then why are you still taking on cases

717
00:30:36,240 --> 00:30:38,010
if you're about to leave the job?

718
00:30:39,160 --> 00:30:40,050
Don't say it. I know.

719
00:30:40,440 --> 00:30:41,660
Ever since you came back from Dongping,

720
00:30:41,720 --> 00:30:43,140
you haven't looked happy at all.

721
00:30:43,400 --> 00:30:44,530
Deep down,

722
00:30:44,640 --> 00:30:46,250
you don't want to come to Beijing,

723
00:30:46,550 --> 00:30:48,570
and you don't want to
quit the job either.

724
00:30:49,030 --> 00:30:50,900
You feel like all of us

725
00:30:51,240 --> 00:30:52,330
are forcing you to do something
you don't want.

726
00:30:53,000 --> 00:30:55,570
So you've been feeling stuck
and aggrieved.

727
00:30:55,720 --> 00:30:58,050
You never actually agreed
to come to Beijing.

728
00:30:58,550 --> 00:31:00,050
Then what was all that acting about?

729
00:31:00,680 --> 00:31:01,290
I wasn't acting…

730
00:31:01,310 --> 00:31:02,730
Hong Liang, think about it.

731
00:31:02,960 --> 00:31:03,860
What kind of life

732
00:31:04,750 --> 00:31:05,810
do you actually want?

733
00:31:06,760 --> 00:31:07,200
[Hong Liang]

734
00:31:23,270 --> 00:31:23,770
Great.

735
00:31:24,640 --> 00:31:25,900
I've pissed off my "boss at home."

736
00:31:27,920 --> 00:31:28,730
Forgot to tell her.

737
00:31:30,350 --> 00:31:31,140
Can you believe my office?

738
00:31:31,590 --> 00:31:33,660
Just had to send me
on another trip at the last minute.

739
00:31:34,750 --> 00:31:35,290
I figured,

740
00:31:36,240 --> 00:31:37,810
after all these years,

741
00:31:37,880 --> 00:31:40,050
the leadership has treated me
pretty well.

742
00:31:40,750 --> 00:31:43,730
Maybe I can leave on a good note,

743
00:31:43,880 --> 00:31:45,050
so I said yes impulsively.

744
00:31:45,070 --> 00:31:46,530
But right after, I regretted it.

745
00:31:47,270 --> 00:31:49,220
Didn't even know how to explain it
to Min.

746
00:31:50,790 --> 00:31:51,180
Anyway,

747
00:31:51,790 --> 00:31:52,180
I…

748
00:31:52,590 --> 00:31:54,180
I'll finish up this business trip,

749
00:31:54,750 --> 00:31:55,460
then head to Beijing

750
00:31:56,000 --> 00:31:56,940
and meet up with her.

751
00:31:57,480 --> 00:31:57,980
Liang,

752
00:31:58,750 --> 00:31:59,940
you're about to resign,

753
00:31:59,960 --> 00:32:01,620
why they're still giving you work?

754
00:32:02,160 --> 00:32:03,220
I know, right?

755
00:32:04,270 --> 00:32:05,180
Back then,

756
00:32:05,350 --> 00:32:07,220
maybe I wasn't that capable,
so they didn't use me much.

757
00:32:07,240 --> 00:32:08,940
Now that I'm leaving,

758
00:32:09,110 --> 00:32:10,290
maybe they realize I'm actually good,

759
00:32:10,310 --> 00:32:11,220
so they keep piling on the tasks.

760
00:32:11,240 --> 00:32:12,860
Who gave you this task,

761
00:32:13,640 --> 00:32:14,730
Sun Xiangqun or Zhang Fang?

762
00:32:22,830 --> 00:32:23,380
That's confidential.

763
00:32:26,070 --> 00:32:26,530
Liang,

764
00:32:27,160 --> 00:32:28,730
I've never once heard you say that

765
00:32:28,880 --> 00:32:30,860
to Dad in all these years.

766
00:32:31,160 --> 00:32:32,220
It's because there's a case

767
00:32:32,720 --> 00:32:33,940
I took on a while back.

768
00:32:34,030 --> 00:32:36,220
It's been dragging on,

769
00:32:36,350 --> 00:32:37,490
and now something new has come up,

770
00:32:38,000 --> 00:32:39,180
so I've got no choice
but to deal with it.

771
00:32:40,160 --> 00:32:40,620
Hong Liang.

772
00:32:41,640 --> 00:32:42,570
Tell me,

773
00:32:43,440 --> 00:32:45,090
is it that the case needs you,

774
00:32:45,640 --> 00:32:47,220
or you need the case?

775
00:32:49,160 --> 00:32:50,530
There'll always be another case.

776
00:32:52,070 --> 00:32:52,860
But you only have

777
00:32:53,960 --> 00:32:54,620
one family.

778
00:32:55,400 --> 00:32:56,460
So I hope

779
00:32:57,310 --> 00:32:58,330
you'll really figure out

780
00:32:59,270 --> 00:33:00,180
what matters more.

781
00:33:17,720 --> 00:33:18,380
Liang,

782
00:33:19,110 --> 00:33:20,140
I know it's hard

783
00:33:20,720 --> 00:33:22,050
to just walk away

784
00:33:22,070 --> 00:33:23,380
from something you've done
for over a decade.

785
00:33:25,000 --> 00:33:25,290
Actually,

786
00:33:26,000 --> 00:33:26,730
don't worry about

787
00:33:27,000 --> 00:33:27,700
that job in Beijing.

788
00:33:27,720 --> 00:33:28,770
I can take care of it
with one phone call.

789
00:33:30,240 --> 00:33:31,940
Dou might need

790
00:33:32,680 --> 00:33:33,490
a bit of time to adjust.

791
00:33:33,960 --> 00:33:34,620
But that's easy.

792
00:33:35,000 --> 00:33:36,940
I'll bring her to Beijing myself first.

793
00:33:38,160 --> 00:33:39,380
And don't worry about my sister.

794
00:33:39,400 --> 00:33:40,620
You two have been together for years.

795
00:33:41,000 --> 00:33:42,050
You know her,

796
00:33:43,000 --> 00:33:44,140
spoiled by our old man.

797
00:33:45,960 --> 00:33:47,620
Just find some time to apologize to her,

798
00:33:48,440 --> 00:33:49,810
and it'll all blow over.

799
00:33:50,920 --> 00:33:51,730
As for our father,

800
00:33:52,480 --> 00:33:53,420
I'll go talk to him.

801
00:34:15,510 --> 00:34:16,090
Comrades,

802
00:34:16,920 --> 00:34:18,300
in the course of our recent work,

803
00:34:18,960 --> 00:34:19,690
we found that the Wan Hai case

804
00:34:20,110 --> 00:34:21,650
handled by

805
00:34:22,150 --> 00:34:24,010
Dongping Municipal
People's Procuratorate

806
00:34:24,630 --> 00:34:26,210
may involve a miscarriage of justice.

807
00:34:26,920 --> 00:34:28,490
Some state functionaries,

808
00:34:28,840 --> 00:34:30,940
especially those
in the political and legal system,

809
00:34:31,190 --> 00:34:34,050
are suspected of
protecting local criminal organizations

810
00:34:34,280 --> 00:34:36,900
and colluding with them.

811
00:34:37,280 --> 00:34:39,780
According to preliminary investigation
by the procuratorate,

812
00:34:40,320 --> 00:34:42,340
the nature of the Wan Hai case

813
00:34:42,590 --> 00:34:44,050
is still under question,

814
00:34:44,510 --> 00:34:46,130
with evidence remaining
insufficient and unclear.

815
00:34:46,840 --> 00:34:47,860
During the handling of this case,

816
00:34:48,400 --> 00:34:50,340
a prosecutor died,

817
00:34:51,000 --> 00:34:51,690
workers went missing,

818
00:34:52,320 --> 00:34:54,420
and there were attempts to
cover up the cause of a mine accident.

819
00:34:54,840 --> 00:34:56,490
There is serious suspicion
of criminal offenses,

820
00:34:57,070 --> 00:34:58,940
duty-related crimes
among judicial personnel

821
00:34:59,230 --> 00:35:00,420
and corruption

822
00:35:00,670 --> 00:35:02,690
among state functionaries.

823
00:35:02,960 --> 00:35:04,740
[Suspect Information Record]
Such a serious and harmful criminal case

824
00:35:05,000 --> 00:35:05,980
is rare nationwide.

825
00:35:06,710 --> 00:35:07,490
It must be thoroughly investigated

826
00:35:08,000 --> 00:35:08,380
and eradicated.

827
00:35:09,150 --> 00:35:10,740
With the approval
of the Provincial Party Committee,

828
00:35:11,070 --> 00:35:12,570
a Task Force is hereby established today

829
00:35:12,670 --> 00:35:15,130
to officially investigate
the related criminal leads.

830
00:35:16,070 --> 00:35:17,340
Upon decision by higher authorities,

831
00:35:17,880 --> 00:35:19,460
the 519 Task Force
is officially formed.

832
00:35:20,920 --> 00:35:23,690
It'll be overseen
by Haidong Anti-Crime Office,

833
00:35:24,510 --> 00:35:26,900
led by Haidong Provincial Procuratorate,

834
00:35:27,320 --> 00:35:29,010
with cooperation from
Haidong Senior People Court

835
00:35:29,400 --> 00:35:31,090
and Public Security Bureau.

836
00:35:31,670 --> 00:35:33,420
The Task Force will include
selected officers

837
00:35:33,480 --> 00:35:34,570
from Provincial Procuratorate

838
00:35:34,670 --> 00:35:36,570
and Jiangnan Municipal
Public Security Bureau,

839
00:35:37,150 --> 00:35:39,210
forming a joint investigative team.

840
00:35:39,920 --> 00:35:40,340
Today,

841
00:35:41,440 --> 00:35:42,860
the deputy director
of Jiangnan Police Bureau

842
00:35:43,150 --> 00:35:44,010
and the captain of
Criminal Investigation Detachment,

843
00:35:44,630 --> 00:35:45,650
[Song Yanchuan]
Song Yanchuan,

844
00:35:45,920 --> 00:35:47,610
[Deputy Director of]
has come to attend the meeting

845
00:35:47,960 --> 00:35:48,860
[Jiangnan Public Security Bureau]
along with his fellow officers.

846
00:35:50,190 --> 00:35:51,940
On behalf of
the Provincial Procuratorate,

847
00:35:52,150 --> 00:35:54,650
I warmly welcome all comrades
participating in this operation.

848
00:35:56,280 --> 00:35:57,120
I hereby announce,

849
00:35:57,120 --> 00:35:58,120
[Zhang Fang, Hong Liang, Sun Xiangqun]

850
00:35:58,120 --> 00:35:59,170
Sun Xiangqun,

851
00:35:59,960 --> 00:36:01,380
Commissioner
of the Provincial Procuratorate

